| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5305 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 73f93f0c-8ee8-5697-9c80-844dac3ebf85"
